Photo Frame

This is a simple python project that displays my photo gallery on an old monitor using a raspberry pi 3 or a pico.

Hardware
    *KeyBoard
    *Mouse
    *Monitor
    *Raspberry Pi 3B+/Pico W
    *SD Card 128GB

Software
    *Raspberry Pi OS
    *Python3
    *Tornado Web Server
    *Jinja templates
    *Sqlite3
    *FireFox in --kiosk mode

Setup
    You will need to edit the env vars in photoframe.py to your needs.
    You will also need to edit link paths in run.sh to your needs. 
    The "sh run.sh"